## Tamagui Rules

- Always import from `tamagui`, not from `@tamagui/core` directly
- Use Tamagui layout components for all layout: `YStack` (column), `XStack` (row), `ZStack` (absolute layers)
- Use Tamagui `Text` for all text — never React Native `Text`
- Use Tamagui `Button` for all interactive buttons
- Use design tokens for all spacing, color, and radius — never hardcode pixel values for these
- Allowed hardcoded values: image dimensions, SVG coordinates, Lottie sizes, fixed layout constants
- Common token shorthands:
  - `bg="$background"` — main background (#0a0a0a)
  - `bg="$backgroundStrong"` — card/surface (#111111)
  - `bg="$backgroundFocus"` — subtle highlight (#1a1a1a)
  - `color="$color"` — primary text (#f0ede8)
  - `color="$colorMuted"` — secondary text (#888880)
  - `borderColor="$borderColor"` — borders (#2a2a2a)
  - Accent gold: `'#c8a96e'` (not a token — use literal string)

### Tamagui shorthand props (use always)
```
fos   = fontSize
fw    = fontWeight
lh    = lineHeight
ta    = textAlign
tt    = textTransform
ls    = letterSpacing
ai    = alignItems
jc    = justifyContent
br    = borderRadius
px/py = paddingHorizontal/paddingVertical
mx/my = marginHorizontal/marginVertical
w/h   = width/height
```

